{"tid":2137944,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[果燃台] 全港學校可按原先擬定的日期展開新學年，但以網上授課形式開學","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T05:56:06.000Z","uid":350891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d079ce0d73f2d01be4bd0f21409326156be15cb0","tid":2137944,"uid":350891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"本港第三波武漢肺炎疫情持續爆發，連日確診個案過百宗。由於國際學校及幼稚園一般較早開學，教育局於7月中宣佈不會早於8月17日開學。教育局局長楊潤雄今午召開記者會，宣佈全港學校可按原先擬定的日期展開新學年，但基於疫情，所有面授課程及校內活動將繼續暫停，直至另行通知。學校可用其他模式，包括於網上教學，此安排亦適用於補習社等。<br />\n<br />\n2021 DSEer mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d1e8c28a1aca7ac89149943d31eb53889e1b17","tid":2137944,"uid":274732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"支那雙非仔咪用唔到zoom上堂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61bfd8020f0f50ef24c7cfd3b7c33d810191268","tid":2137944,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94d1e8c28a1aca7ac89149943d31eb53889e1b17","tid":2137944,"uid":274732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"支那雙非仔咪用唔到zoom上堂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"用到"},{"pid":"5f4949259e5046d1f88c662c948775cf0a59ba9f","tid":2137944,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94d1e8c28a1aca7ac89149943d31eb53889e1b17","tid":2137944,"uid":274732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"支那雙非仔咪用唔到zoom上堂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"就係因為要就佢地 所以先用zoom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a73e2bca671a6011b957940e2527b234751265","tid":2137944,"uid":350891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"啲幼稚園都唔知點算<